{"tid":673374,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Daddy捉鬼】摩連奴懷疑曼聯兩王牌詐傷  不想為曼聯出力","createTime":"2018-05-21T19:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T03:23:07.000Z","uid":124292,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"df2e97ee901d42bc8dd2150449a28e5b335de9c3","tid":673374,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T19:14:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-5751025/Jose-Mourinho-furious-Lukaku-Fellaini-did-not-make-effort-play-FA-Cup-final.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle-5751025%2FJose-Mourinho-furious-Lukaku-Fellaini-did-not-make-effort-play-FA-Cup-final.html&d=lsVt4g%2Bcer1Kgt0IXhxS0gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f8a02228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-5751025/Jose-Mourinho-furious-Lukaku-Fellaini-did-not-make-effort-play-FA-Cup-final.html</a><br />\n<br />\n曼聯輸給車路士，無緣足總盃奪冠，這讓摩連奴很生氣。賽後，摩帥將矛頭對準了盧卡古和費蘭尼，認為紅魔是被這兩人給陷害了。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴在比賽後說了一番意味深長的話語，他表示：「當一名球員告訴你無法正選時，剩下的問題就是他能夠出戰多少時間了。我又能怎麼去說服一位自己告訴我沒做好準備的球員上場呢？」摩連奴賽後這番話，指的是費蘭尼和盧卡古。這兩名球員告訴摩連奴，他們尚未完全恢復，沒法正選出戰車路士。<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》透露，摩連奴懷疑盧卡古和費蘭尼的行為，是為了給世界盃留力，摩帥對這二人很失望很生氣。按照盧卡古的說法，他是腳踝有小傷，沒法出戰。而費蘭尼最近三場比賽，都未出場比賽，球員的說法是肌肉拉傷。而《郵報》表示，接近費蘭尼的消息人士透露，他能夠在對陣車路士時出戰。<br />\n<br />\n輸給車路士賽後，摩連奴絲毫沒有對曼聯球員掩飾自己的不滿。《每日郵報》透露，摩連奴在曼聯輸波後，沒有前往更衣室安慰鼓勵球員，他認為曼聯球員現在的心態很「弱勢」。在過去的一年多時間裡，摩連奴不止一次強調「精神力」，他曾多次因此公開批評過盧基-梳爾等人。現在看起來，摩帥還是對曼聯球員的精神力不滿。"},{"pid":"bcc3b445798f5106cb8d68192e1913d493cc51ac","tid":673374,"uid":2169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T19:18:44.000Z","msg":"摩三季is coming"},{"pid":"6bdf3c7c702404ad30e9b55c95b2c16c2139ec68","tid":673374,"uid":3765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T22:08:39.000Z","msg":"收喇啦 就算出到咪又係輸 垃圾"},{"pid":"33ea07e80242285ce679824bf16592b9ea71d22b","tid":673374,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:06:02.000Z","msg":"爽"},{"pid":"06ed07af2ce3d86a0aa243e6c5c6437f501e0188","tid":673374,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:13:22.000Z","msg":"永遠唔知係自己有問題，年紀越大真係會越『盟』塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e936f501999fde835e62c8860a226884c10ce434","tid":673374,"uid":12980,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"咪撚吹啦<br />\n呢兩條友係摩佬契仔<br />\n你話martial shaw就話"},{"pid":"5cc065f5dd70980487fe601f25f4908d7f1f91cf","tid":673374,"uid":58022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e936f501999fde835e62c8860a226884c10ce434","tid":673374,"uid":12980,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:19:49.000Z","msg":"咪撚吹啦<br />\n呢兩條友係摩佬契仔<br />\n你話martial shaw就話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f259b2c3c6eec283e8fa42b1588e4021a4ea4a5c","tid":673374,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"費蘭尼真是王牌"},{"pid":"4d2f0503ae839ee9c0a2f02188464489a2bd6cfc","tid":673374,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"自己無料又係度賴"},{"pid":"b62db7a8dd992b5dd277bf70d7b493d4ff1f5d6d","tid":673374,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"比利時人都迫害daddy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLkk 世3 爆炸頭"},{"pid":"1138165840812b41868d92471c3afbc65de8bbef","tid":673374,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"愛狗逼害摩佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98ff9dbba9cf63bff6e516e7bf6cc9ab0d6caed","tid":673374,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62db7a8dd992b5dd277bf70d7b493d4ff1f5d6d","tid":673374,"uid":84013,"like":0,"di